<br />I think the MMC3 was first used in SMB3 in October 1988. Contra being released in february 1988, the MMC3 wasn't available yet I think.
<br />My Castlevania III has 1992 noted on it, but I think that's the european release date. Note that Konami could use VRC6 only in europe, but since nobody in japan cares about europe, they just scrammed the USA version and adaptated it to PAL timing (and took 2 years doing so).

		

