<br />Sure, but remember that the MMC5 was probably atrociously expensive. Maybe they could sell carts less expensive if they were to use their own VRC6 by porting bankswitch code from japan, and just script, music and title screen code from the USA (and I prefer japanese difficulty by far).
<br />Overall, it's not bad at all like this in MMC5, just a bit less fun because it would be cool to have one more rare board and released only in europe.

		

